#!/bin/sh
# Cursor の Co-authored-by / Made-with トレーラーをコミットメッセージから除去する
COMMIT_MSG_FILE=$1
[ -f "$COMMIT_MSG_FILE" ] || exit 0

grep -v 'cursoragent@cursor.com' "$COMMIT_MSG_FILE" \
  | grep -v 'Co-authored-by: Cursor' \
  | grep -v 'Made-with: Cursor' \
  > "$COMMIT_MSG_FILE.tmp"

mv "$COMMIT_MSG_FILE.tmp" "$COMMIT_MSG_FILE"
exit 0
